title: Zelenskyy tells UN Putin is ‘trying everything’ to prolong Ukraine war; Trump says Nato can shoot down Russian aircraft – live
summary: Ukraine's president has urged China to reconsider its position regarding Russia amid ongoing tensions. title: Dirty Looks review – room after room of utterly filthy fashion
summary: Fashion designers are increasingly showcasing "grimy" styles, such as Balenciaga's £1,400 faux-filthy trainers and JordanLuca's urine-stained jeans. This trend embraces a raw and edgy aesthetic, celebrating imperfection on the catwalk. The overall effect is a provocative and enjoyable exploration of dirt and disarray in high fashion.

title: Cold case solved? Dismembered female body parts reportedly ID’d after 80 years
summary: Oregon state police announced that remains discovered along the Willamette River in April 1946 are believed to belong to a woman known as Oak Grove Jane Doe. The identification offers potential closure on a long-unsolved case. Authorities continue to investigate the details surrounding her death.

title: Trump says he believes Ukraine can regain all land lost to Russia since 2022 invasion
summary: US President asserts that Russia is facing significant economic challenges and urges NATO allies to cease imports of Russian oil. This call is part of a broader strategy to penalize Russia amid ongoing geopolitical tensions. The move aims to further isolate Russia economically in response to its actions.
